#: ../../../security/tpm/xen-tpmfront.rst:115
msgid ""
"Support for the vTPM driver was added in Xen using the libxl toolstack in "
"Xen 4.3.  See the Xen documentation (docs/misc/vtpm.txt) for details on "
"setting up the vTPM and vTPM Manager stub domains.  Once the stub domains "
"are running, a vTPM device is set up in the same manner as a disk or network "
"device in the domain's configuration file."
msgstr ""

